The observed conductivity with 2, 4, and 10 nm thick 2H-MoTe2 at 8 K is deconvoluted using the aforementioned Lorentz and TL components (Fig. 2c) (see Supplementary Information Figures S2, S3, and S4 for additional fittings at various temperatures between 8 and 350 K). The peak positions (ωi)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
